The man will appear in court on Wednesday after the boy was shot and killed on Sunday afternoon. CAPE TOWN A 22-year old man is expected to be charged for the murder of a 13-year-old boy in Wesbank.The teenager was gunned down yesterday afternoon.The police s Noloyiso Rwexana says: I can confirm that a 22-year-old suspect was arrested on Monday in connection with the murder of a 13-year-old boy in Wesbank. The suspect will appear in the Bluedowns Magistrates Court on Wednesday. (Edited by Masechaba Sefularo)